  - Payment: id, bookingId, clientId, amount, dueDate, status
  - Task: id, title, dueDate, assigneeId, priority, status
  - RevenueSnapshot: bookings, gbv, commission, currency, range
  - Alert: id, priority, message, dueDate
- Database tables should support fast filtering for date ranges, overdue items, and role-based access
- Validation:
  - Ensure responses could be null; sanitize to arrays using data ?? []
